 metre schneier noted that cobhams customers include the governments of algeria brunei ghana pakistan saudi arabia singapore and the united states queens awards for enterpriseedit  cobham surveillance based in segensworth hampshire england received a queens award for enterprise in the international trade category the business – formerly known as domo ltd – tripled its export sales in three years  cobham surveillance based in segensworth hampshire received a queens award for enterprise in the innovation category the award was for the development of its solo wireless digital audio and video link technology that improves safety for bomb disposal teams and law enforcement personnel by increasing the range at which they can effectively operate their robotic bomb disposal equipment  cobham antenna systems based in marlow buckinghamshire received a queens award for enterprise in the international trade category the business – formerly known as chelton ltd – continuously increased export revenues over six years and sells over  of its production overseas sports clubedit the company created cobham sports and social club a members club in merley near the main manufacturing site in wimborne dorset which is used as the ground for merley cobham sports fc see alsoedit companies portal aerospace industry in the united kingdom cobham aviation services australia sargent fletcher cobham technical services  era technology ltd referencesedit  a b c annual report  pdf cobham plc retrieved  april    top  for  defensenewscom retrieved  march    a b obituary sir michael cobham the telegraph  april  retrieved  march    tarrant rushton  the secret airfield retrieved  march    aero history comcast   cobham buys stec corporation flying magazine  feb    cobham buys bae systems division the engineer uk  february    cobham to purchase sparta for m rf globalnet  january    tyco electronics announces agreement to sell its rf components and subsystem business to cobham plc press release tyco  may    